Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:54.26,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.52,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,You're certain that Sunraku was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:04.10,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... I'm pretty sure that \Nwas his character name...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.86,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Mia! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.11,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,That's not a monster, it's a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.90,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.07,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,But it's really scary-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.74,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Scary-looking players are still players!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:24.58,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,So, this player named "Sunraku." \NDo you know where he ha—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.92,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Er, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.79,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.46,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,I think he'd gotten a face full \Nof poison from the Python.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.17,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,He ran off into Secondale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.22,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,And he was half-naked, with a bird's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.51,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he could've changed \Nhis equipment by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.56,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,The mask had such a scary expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.98,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,I thought it was a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.19,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}I almost didn't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:50.73,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he really beat the Ravenous Python \Nwithout visiting the first town...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.94,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Thank you for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.03,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,As an expression of my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.16,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.75,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.75,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.50,Default,Psyger-0,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.63,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.39,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.85,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Not sure, but the emblem on the cape...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.35,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,I think it's from a clan focused on that \Nunique monster, Lycagon the Nightslayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.40,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Unique monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.98,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Lycagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.99,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Unique monsters are a \Nspecial class of monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.07,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,with both an individual name and a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.74,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,Most monsters, when you beat them \Nor capture them or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.37,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,respawn as a new individual after \Na set period of time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:48.88,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,But for the unique monsters, there's \Nonly one of each in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:54.88,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Rumor says there's seven of them in {\i1}SLF{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.43,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\an8}but we don't even know the spawn \Ncriteria for most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.76,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,{\an8}For each of these unique \Nmonsters, called "Colossi,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:07.02,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,lots of top players have formed \Nclans focused on taking them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.02,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.77,Default,Mia,0,0,0,,So they're just really rare monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.49,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,That's about what it boils down to, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:19.03,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,The issue is how abnormally strong they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.41,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,See, it's been a year since the game started,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.45,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,but even with a playerbase \Nof over 30 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.50,Default,Reiji,0,0,0,,not one person has defeated \Na single unique monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:41.47,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unique monster, Lycagon the\NNightslayer, encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Unique... monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.66,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}As damn tough as those Redcaps were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}it blew 'em away in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}One hit from that and I'm a goner, I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You unique monsters don't have \Nmuch going for you, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That was freaking close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:06.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad I spent all night grinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an8}If I hadn't learned Perfect Parry, \NI'd be totally dead right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.11,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}One second's lapse and I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Better go all-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,How'd you like that, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It disappeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Where'll it come from next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's teleporting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.11,Default,Frog,0,0,0,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thing's pelt is tougher than \Nthe Ravenous Python's scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been whaling on the thing for over \Nfive minutes without taking a hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:37.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thing's so tough, I don't think \NI'm actually doing any damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:45.42,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretty sure I've landed a \Nhundred... no, two hundred crits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Vorpal Choppers, which started out close \Nto mint, are already falling apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.34,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't find a softer \Nspot to land a hit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}my weapons are gonna crap out before I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}this thing's way out of the league \Nof what I can fight right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.19,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's the way I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:09.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what makes it the god-tier \Ngame, {\i0}Shangri-La Frontier{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This spine-tingling intensity that \Nmakes me feel like I'm on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not possible to enjoy \Na game more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bugs! Garbage balance! Absurd spawn rates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:26.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a gamer who's made it \Nthrough all those trash games!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}And since I know you don't \Nhave a bugged-out hitbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way in hell I'm \Ngonna throw in the towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm too far for its attack to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.70,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's roaring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What'd it do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.39,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What'd it hit me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reality's a harsh mistress, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:30.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not gonna suddenly \Nlearn an awesome new skill
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:34.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}or get saved by a run-in from some \Nmysterious high-level player...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.78,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of that cinematic stuff for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually... I did get one break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow, after a hit like that, \NI've got an HP remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's gotta be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You're absurdly strong, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:00.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But that absurdity was \Nintentionally coded into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:04.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You're exactly as strong as \Nyour creators wanted you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.02,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a {\i0}beatable{\i1} absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn about \Nthe final boss or the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It might not be now, but someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.79,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat you, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.79,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You better not let anyone \Nbeat you before then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Lycagon the Nightslayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:07.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Lycagon's Mark (Curse)."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:25.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Equipment cannot be equipped to the body \Npart afflicted with Lycagon's Mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Am I... screwed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lycagon's Mark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}What the heck is this crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I can't equip stuff to my torso or legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.80,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That piece of crap wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It shows up out of nowhere, \Nchomps me, and marks me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,With a curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:03.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You can't just destroy a \Nguy's equipment like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.39,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Equipment cannot be equipped to the body \Npart afflicted with Lycagon's Mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Monsters of lower level than the \Nafflicted character will flee."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Conversations with NPCs will be affected \Nby the presence of Lycagon's Mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.94,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"The afflicted body part gains \Nresistance to magic effects."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"The curse can be removed \Nthrough the prayers of a Saint
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:23.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,or the defeat of the curse's caster"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:33.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The kind of curse where you gotta \Ndestroy the root to be rid of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.51,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Nice weather today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.97,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,This is trash game bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.94,Default,Mobs,0,0,0,,Going around half-naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:56.44,Default,Mobs,0,0,0,,So lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.65,Default,Mobs,0,0,0,,Couldn't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.82,Default,Mobs,0,0,0,,What a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:13:59.94,Default,Mobs,0,0,0,,Is it a reference to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sunraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Remember the three principles \Nyou learned from trash games:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Patient mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Unbreakable spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.50,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And cool-headed judgment.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.92,0:14:24.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Looks like you rack up a lot of experience \Nfrom just fighting a unique monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Which means I leveled up quite a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,buffed up my skills and got lots \Nof stat points to allocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,This might be a good time to define my build.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'd better distribute these \Nfifty points carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Vitality, 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I made myself a glass cannon \Nwho can die in one hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But what else could I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm locked out of two out \Nof four of my armor slots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Spending points on vitality \Nis like pissing in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Same with my HP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna have to cover \Nwith speed and stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And my best stat is a 65 in luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The reason I got off then \Nwith one HP remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That's gotta be my luck at play... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.72,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's gotta do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean... I've been through \Nenough hell already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:21.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's okay to turn to luck for help, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What's a rabbit doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I-Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,a Vorpal Bunny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.29,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.04,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Though, it doesn't look quite the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hang on, does this game let \Nmonsters spawn in towns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Get back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,No, that outfit it's wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.98,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That's not just some Vorpal Bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I bet if I catch it, I'll get a rare item!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:05.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's gotta be that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.58,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yes! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.46,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"Unique Scenario: Invitation from Rabituza"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.77,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I get it. I saw this on \Nthe game guide site...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:44.82,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,"{\i1}SLF{\i0} has a sweeping main story \Nabout the exploration of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.65,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's also got a huge \Nnumber of side quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.49,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}One subset of these is \Ncalled 'unique scenarios,'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.91,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}mystery scenarios whose \Nunlock times, locations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:59.25,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}contents, and flags aren't publicly known."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:04.75,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So the equipment, skills, and spells you \Ncan acquire in these unique scenarios...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.26,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}...are said to all be top-class."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:13.47,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's not unusual to see clans \Nsearching desperately to find
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.68,Flashback,Rakuro,0,0,0,,{\i1}these unique scenarios, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,To encounter one this \Nearly in my playthrough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Is this the result of dumping \Nmy stat points into luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.77,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I won't let this chance slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:57.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.11,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Everywhere I look...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's Vorpal Bunnies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:11.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Did I end up in a monsters' lair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.70,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,My fondest welcomes to you, Sunraku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.28,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I've {\i1}dearly{\i0} wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.21,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,All of Rabituza is abuzz about you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.21,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Despite your great personal weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.92,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,you had the courage to attempt \Nthe Nightslayer all on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:36.22,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,And the skills to continue striking perfect \Ndeadly blows without taking a single hit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.72,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,You are the embodiment of the vorpal soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,V-Vorpal soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.81,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,If only I could be like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.02,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,B-But I barely left a scratch on the thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.52,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Only because it's so very, very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.94,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,The Night Emperor is a Colossus,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.74,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,capable of gobbling down \Nwyverns like a midday snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.99,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,That you are even here \Nspeaking to me now suggests
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:00.37,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,you are one of the pioneers \Nunder the Divinity's protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Boy, this bunny loves to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.04,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,And those marks upon your body prove that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.62,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,the Night Emperor regards \Nyou not as mere prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.21,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,but as a fellow being!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.96,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not the first game I've \Nplayed where the monsters talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this thing an NPC?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems pretty focused on Lycagon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, that one trait of the Mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.77,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this what it was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.69,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,And in light of your great \Ndeeds, my Da— ahem—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.02,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,our boss would very much \Nlike to speak with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.28,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,hence why I was sent to fetch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.70,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,M-Meet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:40.58,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I hope this isn't revenge for all the \NVorpal Bunnies I killed, Miss, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.33,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.58,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,You may call me Emul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this thing really AI?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can even guess what I was gonna ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.92,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,You may rest easy, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.18,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Our boss is {\i1}far{\i0} above petty \Nmatters like revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Look at that craftsmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.74,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Quite a number of humans visit Rabituza,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.95,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,but you'll be the first \None to visit the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The first one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.50,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:32.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Is this a unique scenario only I know about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:36.80,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,When that piece of crap dog gave me \Nthis Mark, I was pretty worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:40.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But it looks like my luck's \Nfinally turned around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.80,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Come, come! Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.56,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Daddy—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.02,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I mean, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:54.19,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I brought the human bearer of \Nthe vorpal soul to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What kind of show of gratitude—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.21,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:22.55,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,So, you're the one that pup beat\Nup and took a piss on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.93,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.93,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,You people lose your vorpal soul so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:33.15,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,I'd assumed you were all hopeless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.32,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,Looks like at least one \Nof you's got some promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.99,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.83,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,Mind giving me a bit of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.59,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,I'm the boss here in Rabituza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:01.17,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,The name's Vysache.
